e":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a406016e001fda7205ace1023d4ad987d96e2ac","tid":2192551,"uid":287707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc66178bdd85becb9bc0540188456232d09df9d5","tid":2192551,"uid":318825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d050f817edb69a37b712c1e3392bfccb9a099ed","tid":2192551,"uid":287707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以唔好用呢個名？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"本身想叫驚驚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"而家我真係驚驚啊"},{"pid":"279320137314f0beeda6132d622a61d4665addde","tid":2192551,"uid":370479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"記憶 係最痛苦"},{"pid":"2404387092b0a0a5b2307d5836b08114c54b086d","tid":2192551,"uid":172321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"拍咗幾耐，有冇一齊去過旅行<br />\n我上星期都分咗，前度女友近呢兩個月都係到冷暴力，我最後忍唔住所以講咗分手<br />\n利：final year學生，拍咗1年4個月，上年年尾仲一齊去埋旅行，不過撕爛塊臉佢都無回頭，決意放低"},{"pid":"4f521a216d9e069668d756f8dd4feffe9e3ef9ac","tid":2192551,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d050f817edb69a37b712c1e3392bfccb9a099ed","tid":2192551,"uid":287707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0c0ed3a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}